Registration
************

   This is an unregistered version of Ensemble Verbes.  The full
version has many @{"additional features" Link "AdditionalFeatures"}.

   @{"The French Student's Dictionary & Guide" Link "Dictionary"} is available to registered
users for an additional $5.  Anyone may purchase copies of the
dictionary separately for $10.

   Registered users will be notified of major upgrades to Ensemble
Verbes, and will receive them upon request for a minimal charge.
When new programs are available, registered users will be able to
receive them at a reduced cost.

   To register, please complete the following form and mail it to the
address below with a cheque or money order in Canadian or U.S. funds.
Prices shown are in Canadian funds.

